id: Quán lý vũ khí trang bị Cụm_SLTheoTinhTrang

actionConfiguration.body:
SELECT 
    tinh_trang,
    COUNT(*) AS so_luong_thiet_bi
FROM 
    public.e_thiet_bi_mang
GROUP BY 
    tinh_trang
ORDER BY 
    tinh_trang DESC;
